<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Letter of Resignation</title>
</head>
<body>

<br>${company}
<br> ${address}
<br>${city} ${state}, ${zip}
<p>
<p>Dear ${boss},</p>
<p>I am writing to notify you that I am resigning from my position as ${position} within ${company}. My last day of employment will be ${lastDay}.</p>
<p>I appreciate the opportunities I have been given during my time with your company, as well as your professional guidance and support.  My decision to leave was not one I took lightly.</p>
<p>I wish you and ${company} the best of success in the future.
<p>If I can assist with the transition, please do let me know.
    <br>
<p> Very sincerely,
    <br>
    <br>
<p>${fullName}</p>

</body>
</html>
